msgid "<1.so>Groooooaar..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk03"
msgid "<1.so>Mmrraggghrr..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk04"
msgid "<1.so>Time to get ready for tomorrow..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk05"
msgid "<1.so>You should hurry up and head back, too."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid "<1.so>Don't follow me! I'm on my way to work!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk07"
msgid "<1.so>Are you...<2.pa>following me?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Um, excuse me?<2.pa> Are you running around\n"
"trying to <3.se_co>eavesdrop <4.re_co>on everyone's\n"
"conversation?<5.pa> And so obviously...?\n"
"You really need to work on your craft."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (red)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh, and that reminds me, my little one\n"
"was gabbing about something interesting\n"
"the other day...\n"
"Apparently a<2.se_co> young girl<3.re_co> was seen going\n"
"in and out of the <4.se_co>Hateno Ancient\n"
"Tech Lab<5.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk11"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh, weird.<2.pa> Think they adopted or\n"
"something?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: pause (short)
#. 6: pause (short)
#. 7: pause (short)
#. 8: pause (longer)
#. 9: sound
msgctxt "talk12"
msgid ""
"<1.so>But the <2.se_co>director<3.re_co>...<4.pa>just doesn't seem the\n"
"adopting type, you know?\n"
"\n"
"I just have to wonder if the girl is... <5.pa>\n"
"ac-<6.pa>tu-<7.pa>ally... <8.pa><9.so>No, that can't be."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk13"
msgid ""
"<1.so>What's your problem?!<2.pa> How DARE you \n"
"try to <3.se_co>eavesdrop<4.re_co>? Mind your business!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk14"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Honestly, young people these days...<2.pa>\n"
"What kind of scamp just <3.se_co>eavesdrops <4.re_co>\n"
"like it's no big deal? How rude."
msgstr ""

